From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


 Note: Please do not add templates to this category; instead, use one of its subcategories.  The pages listed in this category are templates. 
 This page is part of Wikipedia's administration and not part of the encyclopedia. 
show
 Further template category notes 

 This category contains pages in the template namespace. It should not be used to categorize articles or pages in other namespaces. Note: Select the proper categories given in Category:Wikipedia template categories instead.By default, templates used primarily in article space would just fill up a set aside subcategory for that purpose (i.e. any "category:article namespace templates") analogous to the below subcats. Hence, not burdening the system with such useless listing has been the road traveled.

 
 
Categories of templates grouped by the namespace in which they are intended to be used are listed here. Do not add templates directly to this category; use an appropriate subcategory.

See also the categories Namespace manipulation templates and Pages with templates in the wrong namespace
